<lb ed="L" n="0267a12"/><cb:div type="note"><entry><form>夯</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0267a1202" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">呼講切壑上聲人用力以堅舉物</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>擗</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0267a1216" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">匹歷切音霹析也擘開也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>絓</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0267a1227" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">古書
<lb ed="L" n="0267a13"/>切音卦與挂同懸也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>黮</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0267a1310" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">與葚同桑實也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form><term rend="no_nor"><g ref="#CB17540">󴒄</g></term></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0267a1317" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">離珍切同麟牝麒也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>襏<anchor xml:id="beg_8f" type="cb-app"/>襫<anchor xml:id="end_8f"/></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0267a1331" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline"><unclear></unclear>
<lb ed="L" n="0267a14"/>末切音撥下施隻切音釋襏<anchor xml:id="beg_90" type="cb-app"/>襫<anchor xml:id="end_90"/>雨衣也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry></cb:div></cb:div>
